{"tid":378412,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I][Gen2][Raid] Pokemon Go (15) 超夢夢即將登場","createTime":"2017-08-28T13:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T00:30:14.000Z","uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09e318db958c4f1578db90c6a71a1fe640432475","tid":378412,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">此Post嚴禁外掛飛狗參與討論</span><br />\n&quot;不敗皇者-曼聯&quot; (ID: 24121) 為爛口外掛賤種飛狗<br />\n請大家遠離，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">切勿回覆/引用</span>此賤種飛狗一切回應</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另一位空中飛人：&rdquo;人生失敗&rdquo; (ID: 592)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/150821_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F150821_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg&h=1d87430c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>絕對不要用幸福蛋</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21bd3046f5b93419c653ffcdd91bc4d4f6e75de","tid":378412,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:00:47.000Z","msg":"使用入場券，可以無限挑戰直到贏為止 或 2小時出現時間完畢。<br />\n <br />\n人數不足: 無論已入場或仍在等候入場，都可以都可以離場再入。已入場按離開返回上圖橙色畫面，請再按上方練束。<br />\n <br />\n未選精靈: 入場後按離開，會返回上圖橙色畫面，盡快選好精靈入場，會重返原本果場。<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全部瀕死: 返回上圖橙色畫面，重選過6隻/補血再戰，會重返原本果場，不會扣卷！</span></span></strong><br />\n <br />\nRaid Battle知多啲<br />\n<a href=\"http://telegra.ph/Raid-06-24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2FRaid-06-24&d=3qOPseODpM7ZIU44cv8JVPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b0ca08a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://telegra.ph/Raid-06-24</a><br />\n <br />\n自己入Telegram Group留意你該區有咩四星Raid打<br />\nPok&eacute;mon Go 香港頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKPGC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKPGC&d=3qOPseODpM7ZIU44cv8JVPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7c631349\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKPGC</a>"},{"pid":"600236e0c40fedfb0156079238b0c8f9b237e18c","tid":378412,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Raid Battle小知識</span></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Raid 只會在0600-2045之間出現</span></strong></span><br />\n <br />\n平日就返工前、放飯、下午茶、收工、尾水都會多人打<br />\n <br />\n每日可以獲得一次免費挑戰券，不能同時擁有兩張免費券，記得每日都用。<br />\n <br />\n可以喺道館上面嘅 Pok&eacute;Stop 攞到，同一日想再挑戰要買入場券(Premium Pass)。<br />\n各地區群組會提供附近 Raid 發生地點，請多加留意 Pinned Message，唔好撳右上角嘅 X，確保獲得最新資訊。<br />\n <br />\n唔該:<br />\n急凍鳥用 班吉拉、滾動岩、火系打、次選其他好大力嗰啲(唔好用肥大唔該)<br />\n利基亞用 班吉拉、電系打、次選其他好大力嗰啲。<br />\n你無卡比背背，幸福蛋最多用1隻，放喺隊伍最後1格，咁樣可以撐耐啲。但係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">只係放係最尾，因為幸福蛋打RAID既攻擊力同海馬一樣！ 無用架！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g95Ug3t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fg95Ug3t.png&h=079869be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">常見問題</span></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Q：</span></strong>請問團體戰免費卷每日一次個計法係<br />\nA. 第一日用過，到夜晚12點就可以再拎<br />\nB.第一日下晝3點用過，就一定要第二日3點先可以再拎<br />\n <br />\n係邊種？<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Ａ：</strong></span>接近A<br />\n <br />\n但正確D黎係<br />\n每日過左12點, 而你手上冇卷, 你就會轉到1張<br />\n換句話講, 如果你尋日張卷未用, 你打左手上張卷, 你變左0卷, 之後你就會轉到1張返黎, 你可以即日再用埋佢"},{"pid":"2e1be707f2e91156427075b21e74